Sri Lanka to Set Up Zone to Manufacture Pharmaceutical Products

-- B y   A n u s h a   O n d a a t j i e   a n d   A s a n t h a   S i r i m a n n e
-- 
2011-10-20T05:46:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/sri-lanka-to-set-up-zone-to-manufacture-pharmaceutical-products.html
Sri Lanka  plans to set up a
dedicated industrial zone to manufacture pharmaceutical
products, the government’s information department said in a
statement.  More than ten “reputed” pharmaceutical companies have
expressed willingness to invest in the zone in island nation’s
Kurunegala district, the statement said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anusha Ondaatjie in Colombo at 
